1
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:26,890
♪Lights of swords are like
a splash of rivers♪

2
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:34,320
♪Shadows of swords cover the seasons♪

3
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:38,090
♪The clear water cuts off the gorge♪

4
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:42,190
♪Which is facing the armed army♪

5
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:45,780
♪Missing a pot of cold wine♪

6
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:49,590
♪Drunk in the middle of sand♪

7
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:53,520
♪The place of peace of mind
is my hometown♪

8
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:57,240
♪But my hometown is by your side♪

9
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Who forgets about the grudges
in the past♪

10
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:04,920
♪Don’t blame the west wind
for your tears♪

11
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,700
♪To meet and to part are like a dream♪

12
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:12,610
♪Well-armed with armor and weapons♪

13
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:16,960
♪Where the surging river is going♪

14
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:22,960
♪Together we go to the end of the world♪

15
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:29,980
=Legend of Fei=

16
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,940
=Episode 31=

17
00:01:34,830 --> 00:01:37,630
You’re foul-mouthed.

18
00:01:37,630 --> 00:01:38,870
I can’t wait to teach you a lesson,

19
00:01:38,870 --> 00:01:41,040
bastard!

20
00:01:42,870 --> 00:01:43,950
I’ll get them out

21
00:01:43,950 --> 00:01:44,870
and be right back.

22
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,040
Sure.

23
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:48,910
Follow me.

24
00:01:49,270 --> 00:01:50,400
Let’s go.

25
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,950
You’re dead!

26
00:01:58,720 --> 00:01:59,800
Phoenix!

27
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,760
You think you can get away

28
00:02:02,910 --> 00:02:04,080
just like that?

29
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:05,910
I... I’ve

30
00:02:05,910 --> 00:02:07,080
explained everything

31
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,600
already.

32
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:10,320
All that is true.

33
00:02:10,670 --> 00:02:13,110
Do you mean how unthankful

34
00:02:13,110 --> 00:02:14,720
and ungrateful you are?

35
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:16,910
Were my brother still alive,

36
00:02:16,910 --> 00:02:19,030
you... you’d be showing him disrespect.

37
00:02:19,030 --> 00:02:20,630
Shut your pie hole!

38
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,910
Huo Liantao,

39
00:02:22,910 --> 00:02:24,520
who are you

40
00:02:24,830 --> 00:02:27,110
to lecture me?

41
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:29,270
Listen,

42
00:02:29,270 --> 00:02:31,000
I can’t care less

43
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,800
about respect,

44
00:02:33,830 --> 00:02:36,240
let alone your brother is already dead.

45
00:02:36,550 --> 00:02:38,190
Were he not,

46
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:39,440
and standing right before me,

47
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,470
he couldn’t stop me

48
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:41,550
from killing you!

49
00:02:41,550 --> 00:02:42,670
You...

50
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:56,190
Phoenix,

51
00:02:56,470 --> 00:02:59,160
I’ve finished him for you.

52
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:01,110
You’re welcome.

53
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:04,520
Just give me the Seal.

54
00:04:01,830 --> 00:04:03,470
Phoenix,

55
00:04:03,470 --> 00:04:05,830
I heard there’s a quick guide

56
00:04:05,830 --> 00:04:08,550
to the 100 Destructive Palms

57
00:04:09,190 --> 00:04:11,030
but the side effect is
the older you get,

58
00:04:11,030 --> 00:04:13,270
the weaker you become.

59
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:16,640
Better take care of yourself.

60
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:19,320
I don’t owe you

61
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:20,830
or Old Master Huo

62
00:04:20,830 --> 00:04:22,720
anything.

63
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:25,510
Why risk your life?

64
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:32,790
You castrated dog!

65
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:36,000
That Seal belongs to the Huo family.

66
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,000
I will get it back.

67
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:43,200
Report!

68
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:44,670
Lord Chu,

69
00:04:44,670 --> 00:04:46,390
someone helped The Third Prince escape.

70
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:53,000
I wonder

71
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,390
who is it

72
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:57,040
that got him out of my hand.

73
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,440
The Third Prince called him

74
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:59,550
Xie Yun.

75
00:05:02,550 --> 00:05:05,790
Xie Yun?

76
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:09,640
It’s you, little prince.

77
00:05:10,350 --> 00:05:11,950
Who’d know

78
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:14,720
I’d run into an old acquaintance’s son?

79
00:05:15,230 --> 00:05:16,600
Help!

80
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:19,390
Your Highness. Your Highness.

81
00:05:19,390 --> 00:05:21,110
-Go!
-Leave now!

82
00:05:24,880 --> 00:05:25,640
Stop there!

83
00:05:25,670 --> 00:05:26,390
Don’t!

84
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,110
Let him go.

85
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:28,110
Protect His Highness first.

86
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:29,000
Let’s go.

87
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,550
Thanks, Miss.

88
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:08,720
Xie Yun.

89
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,000
Didn’t I ask you to leave?

90
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,110
Why are you back?

91
00:06:11,110 --> 00:06:12,670
We got lost in the woods

92
00:06:12,670 --> 00:06:13,880
and circled back

93
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,760
somehow.

94
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,110
Listen.

95
00:06:17,110 --> 00:06:18,270
Follow the servants

96
00:06:18,270 --> 00:06:19,510
in the Huos’ uniforms.

97
00:06:19,510 --> 00:06:21,000
Just go with them.

98
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,110
I can’t.

99
00:06:22,110 --> 00:06:23,110
This place is dangerous.

100
00:06:23,110 --> 00:06:25,160
I can’t leave you two behind.

101
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,350
Your Highness,

102
00:06:26,350 --> 00:06:28,270
never put yourself in danger.

103
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:29,760
Haven’t you learned enough lessons?

104
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:31,000
No.

105
00:06:33,550 --> 00:06:34,600
What should we do now?

106
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,790
There’s no time to think.

107
00:06:35,790 --> 00:06:37,510
It’s too dangerous for him to be alone.

108
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:38,880
Let’s escort him out first.

109
00:06:39,640 --> 00:06:40,550
Sure.

110
00:06:44,230 --> 00:06:45,920
Huo Liantao’s manor

111
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:48,000
is as odd as can be.

112
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,510
Better get out of here first.

113
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:54,140
(Huo’s Manor)

114
00:07:13,110 --> 00:07:14,510
Where’s Ding Kui?

115
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:16,270
He’s inside.

116
00:07:45,510 --> 00:07:46,830
We’ve got company.

117
00:07:47,830 --> 00:07:49,790
You’re such a jinx

118
00:07:49,790 --> 00:07:51,390
as your name Meimei suggests.

119
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:52,510
We’re like

120
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:54,390
crow bait now.

121
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:57,790
You’re right.

122
00:07:58,070 --> 00:08:00,070
I hate to say this,

123
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:01,920
but what a small world!

124
00:08:02,510 --> 00:08:03,550
What do you mean?

125
00:08:04,070 --> 00:08:05,390
-You...
-I know.

126
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,390
I shouldn’t fight

127
00:08:06,390 --> 00:08:07,600
or use my energy.

128
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:08,920
But Fei,

129
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:10,880
there are things

130
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:12,040
we must do

131
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,950
ourselves.

132
00:08:14,670 --> 00:08:16,720
But... but there’s no key.

133
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,510
I know what to do.

134
00:08:20,510 --> 00:08:22,880
Little prince,

135
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:33,000
what are you two whispering about?

136
00:08:34,230 --> 00:08:36,150
You’re lucky

137
00:08:36,150 --> 00:08:38,350
to have lived so long

138
00:08:38,350 --> 00:08:41,110
with Bone-chilling in your system.

139
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:46,320
Look at you two lovebirds.

140
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:48,640
You don’t want to die, do you?

141
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:53,440
I’m sure you know

142
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:55,400
only one of us

143
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:57,590
can survive by the end of the day.

144
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:01,880
That’s bold.

145
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,030
Xie Yun.

146
00:09:04,030 --> 00:09:04,710
Your Highness!

147
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:08,760
Your Highness!

148
00:09:11,350 --> 00:09:12,670
Little prince,

149
00:09:12,670 --> 00:09:13,520
no,

150
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:14,880
Your Highness,

151
00:09:15,710 --> 00:09:17,080
the Chens

152
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:19,670
dethroned the Xiaos,

153
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:22,200
yet here you’re
serving your enemy’s son.

154
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:24,200
How stupid you are!

155
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:26,200
What about you?

156
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:28,030
You betrayed my father,

157
00:09:28,030 --> 00:09:29,590
killed my uncle

158
00:09:29,590 --> 00:09:30,880
and defected to the enemy.

159
00:09:31,230 --> 00:09:32,880
How has Demons Manor

160
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,080
treated you?

161
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:38,320
Eunuch Chu, since you’ve recognized me,

162
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:39,880
it’s time

163
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,400
for us

164
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:43,000
to settle the score once and for all.

165
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,400
Bring it on!

166
00:09:45,760 --> 00:09:49,470
The legendary Cloud-impelling Palm

167
00:09:49,470 --> 00:09:51,080
is nothing

168
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,760
but a useless skill to me.

169
00:09:53,150 --> 00:09:55,080
Your master

170
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:58,350
only made you weak and soft.

171
00:09:58,640 --> 00:09:59,840
What now?

172
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:02,640
You think your soft skill

173
00:10:02,640 --> 00:10:04,470
and borrowed energy

174
00:10:04,470 --> 00:10:06,400
can beat me?

175
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:14,320
Your Highness!

176
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,280
Calm down.

177
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:27,230
Fei!

178
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:31,960
Your turn.

179
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:49,000
Not bad!

180
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,670
Interesting!

181
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,440
Who are you?

182
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:06,320
What’s your name?

183
00:11:07,110 --> 00:11:08,280
A nobody

184
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:09,320
not worth mentioning.

185
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:37,550
It’s open!

186
00:11:38,230 --> 00:11:39,030
Yes.

187
00:11:45,710 --> 00:11:46,640
Found it.

188
00:11:47,350 --> 00:11:48,960
Miss Zhou, look.

189
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:49,880
Why are you still here?

190
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:50,840
Go!

191
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:54,840
Zichen,

192
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,710
give me your weapon.

193
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,200
Your Highness!

194
00:12:05,590 --> 00:12:06,880
Go back and study hard.

195
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:08,590
Don’t waste time on other things.

196
00:12:08,590 --> 00:12:09,550
Xie Yun.

197
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:10,320
Go!

198
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:10,910
-Get him out of here.
-Let’s go!

199
00:12:10,910 --> 00:12:11,760
No.

200
00:12:11,760 --> 00:12:12,590
-Come!
-Xie Yun!

201
00:12:12,590 --> 00:12:13,470
-Xie Yun!
-Let’s go, Your Highness.

202
00:12:13,470 --> 00:12:14,320
Let me go!

203
00:12:16,110 --> 00:12:17,030
Miss Zhou!

204
00:12:17,030 --> 00:12:18,350
-Young Master.
-Xie Yun!

205
00:12:19,110 --> 00:12:20,280
Let’s go!

206
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:22,910
Come on, Young Master!

207
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:46,760
Look how selfless you are!

208
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:48,110
Why didn’t you leave

209
00:12:48,110 --> 00:12:49,840
with that girl?

210
00:12:51,230 --> 00:12:52,670
She wouldn’t

211
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:54,200
even if I asked her to.

212
00:12:54,910 --> 00:12:56,230
If you’re

213
00:12:56,230 --> 00:12:57,880
reluctant to leave,

214
00:12:58,230 --> 00:12:59,520
then stay.

215
00:12:59,910 --> 00:13:01,230
Alright.

216
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:04,230
I can spare some time

217
00:13:04,230 --> 00:13:06,080
for you.

218
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:14,960
Your Highness!

219
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:17,030
Your Highness, don’t worry.

220
00:13:17,030 --> 00:13:17,910
Miss Zhou

221
00:13:17,910 --> 00:13:19,670
won’t let anything happen to Mr. Xie.

222
00:13:19,670 --> 00:13:20,840
Is that

223
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:22,670
Miss Zhou, Zhou Fei?

224
00:13:23,230 --> 00:13:24,030
Yes.

225
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:26,150
The way she wielded the blade

226
00:13:26,280 --> 00:13:27,550
was indeed

227
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:30,110
unforgettable.

228
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:33,520
Your Highness,

229
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:35,200
we should leave now.

230
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:36,350
Your Highness!

231
00:13:36,550 --> 00:13:37,710
Let’s go.

232
00:13:39,550 --> 00:13:41,400
Let’s go, Young Master.

233
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:43,530
Come.

234
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:24,320
I’ll kill you

235
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:26,200
at the cost of my life!

236
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:28,080
Eunuch Chu,

237
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:29,640
you’ll die here!

238
00:15:02,350 --> 00:15:06,110
As soft as Cloud-impelling Palm seems,

239
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:10,080
it’s as powerful as I heard.

240
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:13,960
If we weren’t enemies,

241
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:16,640
this battle

242
00:15:16,640 --> 00:15:18,320
would be the best

243
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:21,280
over the past 20 years.

244
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:24,880
Sadly,

245
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:29,320
you’re still poisoned.

246
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:30,710
You have

247
00:15:30,710 --> 00:15:32,520
used your energy earlier

248
00:15:32,520 --> 00:15:34,640
at the Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

249
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:37,350
That poison

250
00:15:37,350 --> 00:15:40,280
will only go deeper

251
00:15:40,280 --> 00:15:43,230
and worsen your condition.

252
00:15:43,230 --> 00:15:45,000
Soon,

253
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:48,200
your joints will freeze,

254
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:50,200
your veins will be blocked

255
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:52,400
and then...

256
00:15:54,590 --> 00:15:57,200
All that is thanks to Hu Tianying.

257
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,910
Otherwise,

258
00:15:58,910 --> 00:16:01,640
I would’ve been caught

259
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:04,200
at a disadvantage now.

260
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:06,030
How dare you provoke him!

261
00:16:06,030 --> 00:16:07,030
You won’t

262
00:16:07,030 --> 00:16:08,580
get out of here alive!

263
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:07,280
Who are you?

264
00:17:07,800 --> 00:17:09,760
The sole heir to
the Big Medicine Valley,

265
00:17:09,760 --> 00:17:11,640
Ying Hecong!

266
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:14,710
Hu Tianying betrayed us

267
00:17:14,710 --> 00:17:16,230
and defected to Demons Manor.

268
00:17:16,230 --> 00:17:18,430
Then you and Shen Tianshu
massacred all our members!

269
00:17:18,430 --> 00:17:21,190
It’s payback time!

270
00:17:23,590 --> 00:17:25,400
Thank you.

271
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:27,000
Hadn’t you weakened him,

272
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:29,110
I wouldn’t have caught him off guard.

273
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:33,560
Ying Hecong, you...

274
00:17:33,560 --> 00:17:34,820
Fei...

275
00:17:36,710 --> 00:17:38,710
Xie Yun!

276
00:17:40,640 --> 00:17:41,680
Don’t go.

277
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:44,000
The mist is poisonous.

278
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:45,400
That’s called Condensed Dew

279
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:47,040
from snakes.

280
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:47,880
It can vaporize

281
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:48,470
in the air

282
00:17:48,470 --> 00:17:50,800
into colorless and odorless poison.

283
00:17:50,800 --> 00:17:52,830
During your fight,

284
00:17:52,830 --> 00:17:54,950
Eunuch Chu has inhaled a lot of it.

285
00:17:54,950 --> 00:17:56,110
The more skilled one is,

286
00:17:56,110 --> 00:17:58,430
the quicker he or she dies.

287
00:17:58,430 --> 00:17:59,590
Eunuch Chu,

288
00:17:59,590 --> 00:18:01,760
you’re as good as they say.

289
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:03,950
You...

290
00:18:09,060 --> 00:18:12,820
(Seal of Cautiousness)

291
00:18:24,950 --> 00:18:25,880
Xie Yun!

292
00:18:31,350 --> 00:18:32,160
Mr. Li,

293
00:18:32,160 --> 00:18:33,350
there you are.

294
00:18:33,350 --> 00:18:35,040
Are you alright, Madam Nichang?

295
00:18:35,040 --> 00:18:36,040
I’m fine.

296
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:37,920
Have you seen that pig Ding Kui?

297
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:39,230
He’s injured tons of our people.

298
00:18:39,230 --> 00:18:40,760
Master meant to kill him,

299
00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:41,800
but he managed

300
00:18:41,800 --> 00:18:42,920
to escape.

301
00:18:42,920 --> 00:18:43,950
I’m glad you’re here,

302
00:18:43,950 --> 00:18:45,640
or we’ll probably get lost.

303
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:47,310
Enough. This place is dangerous.

304
00:18:47,310 --> 00:18:48,760
Let’s get out of here first.

305
00:18:49,800 --> 00:18:50,830
Let’s go.

306
00:19:24,710 --> 00:19:25,520
Sheng,

307
00:19:25,520 --> 00:19:27,070
you’re out.

308
00:19:27,070 --> 00:19:28,430
Who’s that, brother?

309
00:19:28,430 --> 00:19:29,590
He’s really something

310
00:19:29,590 --> 00:19:31,400
that he clobbered Ding Kui alone.

311
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:32,560
Hadn’t I stopped that bonehead,

312
00:19:32,560 --> 00:19:33,680
he would’ve challenged him.

313
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:34,470
You...

314
00:19:34,470 --> 00:19:35,680
You think I’m that stupid?

315
00:19:36,260 --> 00:19:38,020
All these years,

316
00:19:38,020 --> 00:19:40,180
I’ve never heard of such a figure.

317
00:19:42,060 --> 00:19:43,180
Where’s Zhou Fei?

318
00:19:43,580 --> 00:19:44,500
Isn’t she inside?

319
00:19:44,500 --> 00:19:46,340
I thought you had found her.

320
00:19:46,340 --> 00:19:47,660
She wasn’t there.

321
00:19:47,940 --> 00:19:50,340
Probably left to seize those Demons.

322
00:19:51,020 --> 00:19:52,260
We’d better leave.

323
00:19:52,260 --> 00:19:53,580
Let’s go back to the inn

324
00:19:53,580 --> 00:19:55,380
and ask the Route Gang to look for her.

325
00:20:06,580 --> 00:20:08,900
Xie Yun! Xie Yun!

326
00:20:08,900 --> 00:20:09,550
You...

327
00:20:14,220 --> 00:20:15,740
I’m fine.

328
00:20:15,740 --> 00:20:17,180
Don’t worry.

329
00:20:22,340 --> 00:20:23,270
Take this.

330
00:20:24,620 --> 00:20:25,740
What is it?

331
00:20:25,740 --> 00:20:26,980
The antidote to the Condensed Dew.

332
00:20:26,980 --> 00:20:28,980
You must’ve inhaled some, too.

333
00:20:29,420 --> 00:20:30,340
I know

334
00:20:30,340 --> 00:20:32,500
it’s the unwritten rule

335
00:20:32,500 --> 00:20:33,860
that however skilled

336
00:20:33,860 --> 00:20:35,020
and noble one is,

337
00:20:35,020 --> 00:20:35,700
that person shall be condemned

338
00:20:35,700 --> 00:20:37,420
for poisoning others.

339
00:20:49,380 --> 00:20:50,860
It’s been three years
since I made this poison.

340
00:20:50,860 --> 00:20:52,540
This is the first time I’ve used it.

341
00:20:53,220 --> 00:20:54,700
Hadn’t you

342
00:20:54,700 --> 00:20:55,660
cornered him first,

343
00:20:55,660 --> 00:20:57,460
he would’ve spotted me

344
00:20:57,460 --> 00:20:59,780
the minute I entered the woods.

345
00:21:00,300 --> 00:21:01,620
Thank you

346
00:21:01,620 --> 00:21:03,780
for helping me get revenge.

347
00:21:04,060 --> 00:21:05,900
I owe you two one.

348
00:21:21,060 --> 00:21:22,620
Why is there just one?

349
00:21:23,380 --> 00:21:25,060
You want more?

350
00:21:25,060 --> 00:21:25,980
He...

351
00:21:26,340 --> 00:21:27,820
He doesn’t need it.

352
00:21:27,820 --> 00:21:29,700
Bone-chilling he has

353
00:21:29,700 --> 00:21:32,340
is the most toxic poison.

354
00:21:32,340 --> 00:21:33,980
Nothing else

355
00:21:33,980 --> 00:21:35,340
can hurt him,

356
00:21:35,340 --> 00:21:36,900
including my Condensed Dew.

357
00:21:36,900 --> 00:21:38,100
He can drink it like liquor

358
00:21:38,100 --> 00:21:39,860
if he wants

359
00:21:39,860 --> 00:21:41,040
and nothing will happen.

360
00:21:46,900 --> 00:21:48,050
Mr. Ying.

361
00:21:52,340 --> 00:21:53,740
Please don’t sugarcoat the fact

362
00:21:54,700 --> 00:21:56,660
of being poisoned

363
00:21:56,660 --> 00:21:57,970
by Bone-chilling.

364
00:22:00,740 --> 00:22:02,020
Well,

365
00:22:02,020 --> 00:22:04,060
I’ve already told you

366
00:22:04,060 --> 00:22:05,700
that his days are numbered.

367
00:22:06,540 --> 00:22:07,780
Unblocking his veins

368
00:22:07,780 --> 00:22:10,180
by force

369
00:22:10,180 --> 00:22:11,900
has only injured him more.

370
00:22:12,340 --> 00:22:14,020
There’s no cure.

371
00:22:14,420 --> 00:22:16,300
My hands are tied.

372
00:22:18,940 --> 00:22:19,940
You...

373
00:22:19,940 --> 00:22:22,900
You said you owe us one, didn’t you?

374
00:22:22,900 --> 00:22:24,580
How are you going to repay us?

375
00:22:24,580 --> 00:22:25,420
I will,

376
00:22:25,420 --> 00:22:26,940
of course.

377
00:22:26,940 --> 00:22:28,900
But it has to be within my ability.

378
00:22:28,900 --> 00:22:30,940
Removing his poison

379
00:22:30,940 --> 00:22:32,220
is not.

380
00:22:33,060 --> 00:22:33,820
Hey,

381
00:22:33,820 --> 00:22:35,940
you have one last option.

382
00:22:36,820 --> 00:22:38,140
There’s a temple

383
00:22:38,140 --> 00:22:39,260
one kilometer away.

384
00:22:39,260 --> 00:22:40,540
You can go there to pray to Buddha.

385
00:22:40,540 --> 00:22:42,180
Maybe that will work.

386
00:22:44,140 --> 00:22:46,180
Aren’t you the heir
to the Big Medicine Valley?

387
00:22:47,020 --> 00:22:49,020
You’re worse than a quack!

388
00:22:49,260 --> 00:22:51,660
You’re useless!

389
00:22:51,660 --> 00:22:53,940
I am the heir,

390
00:22:54,780 --> 00:22:56,980
but I’m not a physician.

391
00:22:58,900 --> 00:23:01,420
When master taught us medicine,

392
00:23:01,420 --> 00:23:03,780
I always sneaked out to play.

393
00:23:04,100 --> 00:23:05,740
Later on, all our medical books

394
00:23:05,740 --> 00:23:06,740
were burned

395
00:23:06,740 --> 00:23:08,380
by Hu Tianying and Chu Tianyu.

396
00:23:08,380 --> 00:23:09,820
All that’s left

397
00:23:09,820 --> 00:23:12,020
is me, a good-for-nothing.

398
00:23:18,780 --> 00:23:21,220
I don’t deserve my title.

399
00:23:22,420 --> 00:23:23,780
Is there anything else?

400
00:23:23,780 --> 00:23:24,580
If not,

401
00:23:24,580 --> 00:23:26,220
I’m leaving.

402
00:23:32,260 --> 00:23:33,740
Fei,

403
00:23:35,340 --> 00:23:37,020
everyone

404
00:23:37,300 --> 00:23:38,940
will have to die

405
00:23:38,940 --> 00:23:40,780
sooner or later.

406
00:23:41,020 --> 00:23:42,820
That’s natural.

407
00:24:11,620 --> 00:24:13,740
Where are you taking me?

408
00:24:14,380 --> 00:24:16,220
To pray to Buddha.

409
00:24:19,540 --> 00:24:20,640
You once said

410
00:24:22,100 --> 00:24:23,940
if you were me,

411
00:24:24,980 --> 00:24:28,100
even if you failed eventually,

412
00:24:28,100 --> 00:24:31,100
you’d die with no regrets

413
00:24:31,100 --> 00:24:33,580
and be able to

414
00:24:33,580 --> 00:24:35,800
rest in peace.

415
00:24:36,980 --> 00:24:39,710
I believe you.

416
00:24:41,260 --> 00:24:43,700
What will come will come.

417
00:24:46,740 --> 00:24:49,850
Be brave.

418
00:24:51,020 --> 00:24:53,220
Don’t cry.

419
00:24:53,220 --> 00:24:56,020
Don’t forget what you said.

420
00:24:56,020 --> 00:24:57,040
Shut up!

421
00:25:06,460 --> 00:25:08,260
Fine.

422
00:25:08,260 --> 00:25:09,320
Pretty,

423
00:25:11,500 --> 00:25:13,140
I love

424
00:25:13,140 --> 00:25:15,500
your stubbornness.

425
00:25:18,340 --> 00:25:20,100
Put me down

426
00:25:20,860 --> 00:25:22,760
so that we can talk.

427
00:25:24,460 --> 00:25:26,580
Stop talking!

428
00:25:29,180 --> 00:25:30,580
Fei,

429
00:25:31,380 --> 00:25:33,180
things such as

430
00:25:33,860 --> 00:25:36,460
life and death

431
00:25:37,180 --> 00:25:39,500
are predestined

432
00:25:40,100 --> 00:25:44,060
and unchangeable.

433
00:25:44,820 --> 00:25:46,180
Stop it.

434
00:25:46,180 --> 00:25:47,310
I don’t buy that.

435
00:25:54,580 --> 00:25:55,780
Fei,

436
00:25:58,300 --> 00:25:59,810
I was joking

437
00:26:00,900 --> 00:26:02,840
when I said

438
00:26:04,500 --> 00:26:05,960
I wanted you to be my consort.

439
00:26:07,460 --> 00:26:08,940
Don’t take it seriously.

440
00:26:09,540 --> 00:26:10,900
Forget about that.

441
00:26:10,900 --> 00:26:12,460
Who’d marry...

442
00:26:12,460 --> 00:26:16,780
I’ve never wanted to sit on that chair

443
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:18,550
or become an emperor.

444
00:26:27,100 --> 00:26:28,590
You know, I’ve thought about

445
00:26:29,940 --> 00:26:32,300
my death

446
00:26:33,580 --> 00:26:35,660
and I want to be buried

447
00:26:35,660 --> 00:26:37,770
close to home.

448
00:26:37,940 --> 00:26:39,360
♪Stars flow like river♪

449
00:26:39,380 --> 00:26:41,260
But now,

450
00:26:42,220 --> 00:26:44,620
instead of going back to Jiankang,

451
00:26:45,220 --> 00:26:47,180
I’d rather

452
00:26:47,500 --> 00:26:49,860
go to the Fortress with you

453
00:26:51,940 --> 00:26:53,540
or...

454
00:26:54,140 --> 00:26:56,240
somewhere new.

455
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:58,600
♪Youth is like a sweet dream♪

456
00:26:58,620 --> 00:27:00,680
I wish I’d be born a commoner

457
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:02,390
♪The hope in heart never fades♪

458
00:27:02,410 --> 00:27:05,120
and die as one.

459
00:27:05,130 --> 00:27:07,620
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

460
00:27:07,660 --> 00:27:09,420
Sometimes,

461
00:27:09,420 --> 00:27:10,690
I’d drive you so mad

462
00:27:10,690 --> 00:27:13,240
♪I will never be alone♪

463
00:27:13,260 --> 00:27:14,600
that you’d beat me.

464
00:27:14,600 --> 00:27:17,240
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

465
00:27:17,260 --> 00:27:18,820
I’d run away

466
00:27:18,820 --> 00:27:20,580
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

467
00:27:20,600 --> 00:27:22,100
and come back until you weren’t angry.

468
00:27:22,770 --> 00:27:27,400
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

469
00:27:27,420 --> 00:27:28,840
I’d rather be called

470
00:27:28,840 --> 00:27:30,630
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

471
00:27:30,640 --> 00:27:31,960
henpecked

472
00:27:32,260 --> 00:27:33,280
♪I fear not♪

473
00:27:33,290 --> 00:27:33,930
because

474
00:27:33,930 --> 00:27:35,540
♪To roam the world with you♪

475
00:27:35,580 --> 00:27:37,080
you gave me

476
00:27:37,080 --> 00:27:39,890
♪When I go across the world for you♪

477
00:27:39,900 --> 00:27:41,320
a home.

478
00:27:41,320 --> 00:27:44,240
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

479
00:27:44,260 --> 00:27:45,620
The real world is dangerous.

480
00:27:45,620 --> 00:27:47,640
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

481
00:27:47,660 --> 00:27:49,550
You’ll encounter enemies again

482
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:52,280
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

483
00:27:52,290 --> 00:27:54,360
no matter how skilled

484
00:27:54,520 --> 00:27:58,020
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

485
00:27:58,040 --> 00:27:59,890
or famous you are.

486
00:27:59,890 --> 00:28:04,330
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

487
00:28:04,340 --> 00:28:06,700
Ever since

488
00:28:07,380 --> 00:28:08,360
♪The purest love is unadorned♪

489
00:28:08,370 --> 00:28:11,820
you came back to my cell with those jars

490
00:28:14,820 --> 00:28:16,270
and told me

491
00:28:17,580 --> 00:28:19,540
promise weighs more than your life,

492
00:28:22,060 --> 00:28:23,820
you’ve become

493
00:28:25,060 --> 00:28:26,800
second to none

494
00:28:26,800 --> 00:28:28,440
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

495
00:28:28,460 --> 00:28:30,730
in my eyes.

496
00:28:30,730 --> 00:28:34,670
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

497
00:28:34,670 --> 00:28:39,990
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

498
00:28:39,990 --> 00:28:43,200
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

499
00:28:43,210 --> 00:28:44,180
Fei,

500
00:28:44,820 --> 00:28:46,500
take care.

501
00:28:46,500 --> 00:28:48,300
I’ll see you again

502
00:28:48,300 --> 00:28:50,700
in 20 years.

503
00:28:50,700 --> 00:28:52,700
Wait for me.

504
00:28:53,750 --> 00:28:57,960
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

505
00:28:57,960 --> 00:29:03,000
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

506
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:07,030
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

507
00:29:07,030 --> 00:29:11,380
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

508
00:29:12,080 --> 00:29:19,480
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

509
00:29:19,830 --> 00:29:21,080
♪The purest love is unadorned♪

510
00:29:21,080 --> 00:29:24,920
♪I fear not to roam the world with you♪

511
00:29:25,290 --> 00:29:29,710
♪When I go across the world for you♪

512
00:29:30,060 --> 00:29:33,910
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

513
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:39,220
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

514
00:29:39,220 --> 00:29:43,270
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

515
00:29:43,270 --> 00:29:48,270
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

516
00:29:48,270 --> 00:29:55,600
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

517
00:29:56,100 --> 00:30:00,720
♪The purest love is unadorned♪

518
00:30:52,620 --> 00:30:54,260
What was I doing?

519
00:30:55,300 --> 00:30:56,900
Where am I?

520
00:30:56,900 --> 00:30:58,300
Young lady,

521
00:30:58,900 --> 00:31:01,580
are you living a borrowed life?

522
00:31:01,580 --> 00:31:04,380
How could you do this to yourself?

523
00:31:10,180 --> 00:31:11,740
Didn’t you know

524
00:31:11,740 --> 00:31:13,540
you were poisoned?

525
00:31:13,540 --> 00:31:15,460
The antidote was in your pocket.

526
00:31:15,460 --> 00:31:17,060
Why didn’t you take it?

527
00:31:17,060 --> 00:31:18,020
Were you

528
00:31:18,020 --> 00:31:20,100
(Abbot Tongming Three Immortals of Penglai)
testing your life?

529
00:31:20,100 --> 00:31:21,420
Were you?

530
00:31:22,020 --> 00:31:24,340
He’s as sarcastic

531
00:31:24,340 --> 00:31:26,270
as Xie Yun.

532
00:31:27,900 --> 00:31:28,900
Xie Yun.

533
00:31:28,900 --> 00:31:30,460
Where’s Xie Yun?

534
00:31:35,860 --> 00:31:38,110
Slow down.

535
00:31:39,500 --> 00:31:43,180
You people are always jittery.

536
00:31:45,220 --> 00:31:47,140
Abbot,

537
00:31:47,820 --> 00:31:49,100
where’s that man

538
00:31:49,100 --> 00:31:50,780
with me?

539
00:31:51,180 --> 00:31:53,060
Merciful Buddha.

540
00:32:01,780 --> 00:32:04,740
Miss, where are you going?

541
00:32:04,740 --> 00:32:06,900
I can give you a ride.

542
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:09,220
Where should I go?

543
00:32:10,100 --> 00:32:11,460
What should I do?

544
00:32:19,740 --> 00:32:20,750
Abbot,

545
00:32:21,180 --> 00:32:22,420
do you have liquor?

546
00:32:22,420 --> 00:32:24,340
That’s not in reserve.

547
00:32:24,940 --> 00:32:27,220
A canteen is hanging on the mast

548
00:32:27,220 --> 00:32:29,460
with boiled water.

549
00:32:29,460 --> 00:32:31,420
Feel free

550
00:32:31,420 --> 00:32:33,540
to drink it.

551
00:32:42,700 --> 00:32:44,030
Medicine.

552
00:32:51,900 --> 00:32:54,300
We’re no longer in Lingling

553
00:32:54,300 --> 00:32:55,380
and will be soon

554
00:32:55,380 --> 00:32:58,300
out of this area.

555
00:33:00,500 --> 00:33:03,500
Where are you going next?

556
00:33:03,980 --> 00:33:05,620
Lingling.

557
00:33:06,100 --> 00:33:08,740
I should go back to the inn

558
00:33:08,740 --> 00:33:10,460
to not let Li Yan and Li Sheng worry.

559
00:33:11,460 --> 00:33:13,420
But then what?

560
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:16,260
Continue looking for that Bracelet?

561
00:33:17,460 --> 00:33:19,060
But

562
00:33:19,580 --> 00:33:21,280
he’s gone.

563
00:33:24,420 --> 00:33:26,780
It’s fine if you don’t know.

564
00:33:26,780 --> 00:33:29,740
Just don’t forget
why you came in the first place.

565
00:33:30,100 --> 00:33:31,700
But

566
00:33:33,180 --> 00:33:35,140
I’ve lost him.

567
00:33:35,780 --> 00:33:37,420
No, wrong.

568
00:33:47,220 --> 00:33:48,980
Let me help you.

569
00:33:51,300 --> 00:33:52,980
Can you row?

570
00:33:55,020 --> 00:33:56,620
I can learn.

571
00:33:56,620 --> 00:33:58,980
How can I make this thing go?

572
00:33:59,620 --> 00:34:01,900
Think again

573
00:34:01,900 --> 00:34:03,940
what you’re here for.

574
00:34:03,940 --> 00:34:05,460
Then you’ll know

575
00:34:05,460 --> 00:34:08,180
where you should go next.

576
00:34:18,620 --> 00:34:20,180
Does he know

577
00:34:20,620 --> 00:34:22,940
what he’s talking about?

578
00:34:24,580 --> 00:34:26,540
What happened

579
00:34:27,220 --> 00:34:28,980
between you and that man

580
00:34:28,980 --> 00:34:31,940
is only a chapter in your life.

581
00:34:34,860 --> 00:34:36,460
An accident.

582
00:34:37,420 --> 00:34:38,940
He can’t be

583
00:34:38,940 --> 00:34:40,500
what you’re here for.

584
00:35:06,620 --> 00:35:07,720
At first,

585
00:35:08,540 --> 00:35:09,780
I set out

586
00:35:09,780 --> 00:35:12,020
to run an errand for my parents.

